              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>We now come to an example of a <fr:link href="/jms-00I7/" title="Relation" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00I7/" display-uri="jms-00I7" type="local">relation between multiple sets</fr:link>: we could define a relation <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R\subseteq  \text {Movies}\times \text {Directors}\times \text {Years}\times \text {People}]]></fr:tex> consisting of tuples <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left (m,d,y,p\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> where <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[m]]></fr:tex> is a movie directed by <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[d]]></fr:tex> in year <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[y]]></fr:tex> with <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p]]></fr:tex> as a cast member.</html:p>
